title: Microsoft Office 2010 VL ProPlus English (x64) August 2016
description:
Microsoft Office 2010 VL ProPlus English (x64) August 2016

*** Release Info

- OS: 64-bit editions of Windows Vista SP1/7/8 10 - Server 2003 R2/2008/2008 R2/2012
- Language: English (en-US)
- Channel: Volume License
- Version 14.0.7172.5001 (SP2)
- Architectures: x64
- Proofing Tools: English, French, Spanish
- Updated August 9, 2016

** Customized default setup (slightly modified using OCT - Office Customization Tool)

- Skip EULA
- Added serial number required for installation (key in text file if needed)

*** Bonus folder

- KMSpico 10.2.0
- Microsoft Toolkit
- Classic Menu for Office v5.85 (adds Office 2003 type toolbars and menus to Office 2013)
- Office Tab v9.81 (edit multiple files within a single tabbed window)
- Previous versions uninstallers (Office 2003, 2007)
- ShellNewHandler (easily remove New Microsoft_xxxx in Windows Explorer context menu)

*** Installation

- Delete any previously installed version using the provided uninstallers (recommended, not mandatory)
- Mount / burn / extract ISO file
- Install Office 2010
- Activate using Microsoft Toolkit / KMSpico (recommended)

** Optional

- Classic Menu for Office v5.85 (adds Office 2003 type toolbars and menus to Office 2013)
- Office Tab v9.81 (edit multiple files within a single tabbed window)
- Run ShellNewHandler (easily remove New Microsoft_xxxx in Windows Explorer context menu)
